episodes.title: Priest of The Nine O'clock Service Sex Cult Jailed. #chrisbrain #cult #news #justice ✌️
episodes.description:
In 1986, Brain - then lead singer of a Christian rock band - started a new church service at a large charismatic evangelical church in Sheffield called St Thomas Crookes. It met late at night and soon became known as the Nine O'clock
Service or NOS.
